title: Maryland: Edsall will coach Terps at No. 1 Ohio State
text:
Amid firing reports, Maryland says Randy Edsall will coach Terps at No. 1 Ohio State THE ASSOCIATED PRESS First Posted: October 08, 2015 - 8:34 pmLast Updated: October 08, 2015 - 8:34 pm We also have more stories about: (click the phrases to see a list) 
Organizations: 
Ohio (773) 

COLLEGE PARK, Maryland — Maryland says Randy Edsall will coach the Terrapins at top-ranked Ohio State amid reports that he will be fired. 
"Randy Edsall is our head football coach and he'll be on the sidelines Saturday against Ohio State," the school said Thursday in a statement. 
Maryland is 2-3 overall and 0-1 in the Big Ten this season, the 57-year-old Edsall's fifth at the school. He's 22-33 overall at Maryland after going 74-70 in 12 seasons at Connecticut. 
After the game at Ohio State, the Terrapins have a week off before playing Penn State at home Oct. 24.
